headline: The Bull Case For Trane Technologies (TT) Could Change Following Launch of AI Data Center Thermal System
summary: On October 28, 2025, Trane Technologies announced the launch of the first comprehensive thermal management system reference design engineered specifically for NVIDIA’s Omniverse DSX Blueprint, supporting gigawatt-scale AI data centers and emerging AI factory infrastructure. This milestone integrates digital twin capability to help data center developers aggregate complex 3D data, optimize design, and manage energy, water, and land resources for next-generation scalable AI workloads.
